00:42:39.360 --> 00:42:42.340
Are there snakes or crocs?

00:42:42.750 --> 00:42:44.210
I’m scared.

00:42:45.690 --> 00:42:47.690
Didn’t you say it yourself?

00:42:47.810 --> 00:42:49.150
That in this whole forest,

00:42:49.410 --> 00:42:50.860
I’m the fiercest beast?

00:42:51.560 --> 00:42:53.190
Don’t panic.

00:42:53.320 --> 00:42:56.020
With me, you’ve got nothing to fear.

00:43:02.290 --> 00:43:03.480
Worradej...

00:43:05.550 --> 00:43:07.330
When you’re soaking wet,

00:43:08.720 --> 00:43:11.040
